{"id": 1046, "genre": 1001, "title": "你曾经因为“不想浪费”做出了哪些努力？", "description": "这年头我是这样节俭持家的。（题目来自：Rebecca Gibbon）", "record_count": 2702, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160703152313pC2EITe3SAkhtWfZ.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-06-13T11:13:44Z", "options": [{"id": 89602, "content": "为了不浪费五分钟的午觉，我默默的锁定手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 620309}, {"id": 90898, "content": "永远把要记得饭吃完 哪怕自己已经很饱了.....", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 651629}, {"id": 88854, "content": "吃完剩下的菜和饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 605853}, {"id": 88090, "content": "打包饭菜回家放冰箱一星期后扔掉。", "image": null, "praise_count": 234, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 628970}, {"id": 88091, "content": "默默的剩下菜都吃了胖子就是这样一口一口吃成的", "image": null, "praise_count": 442, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 428469}, {"id": 89115, "content": "不穿的衣服，放到小区衣物回收站……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 499720}, {"id": 88092, "content": "遇到喜欢吃的但又已经很撑了。。不吃又浪费。所以还是吃了。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 302, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 178780}, {"id": 88093, "content": "在餐厅吃不了的饭菜打包回去，仅仅是打包回去", "image": null, "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 504368}, {"id": 88094, "content": "当备胎", "image": null, "praise_count": 64, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 419410}, {"id": 88095, "content": "很显然是下载了咸鱼。然而并没有什么卵用。", "image": null, "praise_count": 96, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 113353}, {"id": 88096, "content": "等了半个小时巴士，最后怕上班迟到，打的了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 251, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 614689}, {"id": 88865, "content": "为了满20返5元，我又凑了17元的东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 645214}, {"id": 88098, "content": "吃撑了", "image": null, "praise_count": 71, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 610576}, {"id": 88099, "content": "剩下一点流量，就不停地用流量刷掌上营业厅，直到确认流量用完了再关掉网络。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 454708}, {"id": 88101, "content": "向购物车里多塞了几百上千的东西，就为了买三免一…", "image": null, "praise_count": 49, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 58260}, {"id": 88102, "content": "以前月底最后一天流量没用完一定要下东西用光即使有WiFi", "image": null, "praise_count": 46, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 632333}, {"id": 88870, "content": "为省邮费而购入非需要物品", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 490309}, {"id": 88103, "content": "节约用水 洗完才洗锅 主要是怕有生之年没水会渴死", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 643912}, {"id": 88104, "content": "满199包邮", "image": null, "praise_count": 409, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 239090}, {"id": 88105, "content": "为了不浪费流量，我只能写到这里了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 127488}, {"id": 88106, "content": "不想浪费", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 641796}, {"id": 88107, "content": "蜜汁执着买的衣服，回来怎么看怎么不喜欢了，硬着头皮穿一次，一整天都不舒服", "image": null, "praise_count": 43, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1493}, {"id": 88108, "content": "下载淘宝。", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 643043}, {"id": 88109, "content": "不愿浪费优惠券，结果因为优惠券浪费更多钱…", "image": null, "praise_count": 146, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 199459}, {"id": 88110, "content": "不浪费，吃撑，经常这样。没事我吃不胖。", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 13689}, {"id": 88113, "content": "从参加工作开始打印未定稿坚持用背面纸一直到现在，只用一面就扔掉，太有罪恶感。", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 613988}, {"id": 88114, "content": "满299包邮……", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 589115}, {"id": 88115, "content": "吃撑了，为了凑单买了没用的东西。", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 643558}, {"id": 88116, "content": "厕纸一面擦好几下才舍得对折", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 456251}, {"id": 90164, "content": "米水用来浇花  泡手", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 641292}, {"id": 88117, "content": "几年前的衣服没有扔", "image": null, "praise_count": 132, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 591216}, {"id": 88885, "content": "吃了很多东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 638269}, {"id": 88118, "content": "面膜敷完了涂手臂涂脚", "image": null, "praise_count": 169, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 239090}, {"id": 89401, "content": "吃吃吃……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 617431}, {"id": 88122, "content": "洗衣服，只漂洗一遍！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 643941}, {"id": 88123, "content": "必须是面膜啊  敷手敷胳膊  哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 609396}, {"id": 88124, "content": "把洗衣服 洗菜的水留下来拖地。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 643957}, {"id": 88125, "content": "月底开了十倍加油包，没用完的都看视频了", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 633207}, {"id": 88126, "content": "外出吃饭时，比正常饭量减三分之一。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 643963}, {"id": 88128, "content": "呵呵", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 609701}, {"id": 88129, "content": "淘宝买三、四十的衣服，回来洗两次就穿不了了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 641970}, {"id": 88130, "content": "发现很多衣服都几乎不穿，所以整理衣柜。然后觉得这件能搭，那件也许会穿。一件都没丢，然后过了大半年，也都没再穿过，呵呵。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 641970}, {"id": 88131, "content": "比如一双鞋，拿去修或换底，以为会继续穿，实际是修好后款式也过时了，成了搁货。", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 597330}, {"id": 88132, "content": "通宵", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 643527}, {"id": 88133, "content": "在吃这方面！恨不得吧隔壁桌吃剩的消灭", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 270432}, {"id": 90693, "content": "留下了一大堆不会再穿的衣服", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 651033}, {"id": 88134, "content": "长胖!!!", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 643995}, {"id": 88136, "content": "拿出手机解了屏，喵了一眼，又放进口袋里。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 644001}, {"id": 88137, "content": "出去吃饭，快结束时，把吃不完的吃下去，很撑！变胖的节奏……", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 620597}, {"id": 88138, "content": "主机坏了 主板没事 想着能够买配件再装一台 谁知都装坏了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 563762}]}